## Key Symbols Reference

| Symbol | Key |
|--------|-----|
| `⌘` | Command (Mac) |
| `⇧` | Shift |
| `⌥` | Option/Alt |
| `⌃` | Control |
| `⇥` | Tab |
| `⌫` | Backspace/Delete |
| `⏎` | Return/Enter |
| `⎋` | Escape |

